2.  Synopsys Commands                                        Command Reference
                                   route_opt

NAME
       route_opt
              Optimizes the current routed design.

SYNTAX
       route_opt

DESCRIPTION
       This command optimizes the current routed design for timing, electrical
       DRC violations, area, and power. It performs legalization and ECO rout-
       ing on the optimized design. By default, power optimization, concurrent
       clock and data optimization, are not performed by  this  command.  How-
       ever,  the  command  performs cross-talk reduction, if Signal Integrity
       (SI) is enabled in the design.  Use application  options  in  the  "SEE
       ALSO" section to enable them.

SEE ALSO
       route_auto(2)
       route_opt.flow.enable_ccd(3)
       route_opt.flow.enable_power(3)

